{"tid":1911341,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係點樣面對親人/好朋友離開?","createTime":"2020-03-05T09:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T23:29:26.000Z","uid":153154,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"558eb5b06dfe77e1c797e10ebe6adeef2923b96a","tid":1911341,"uid":153154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:16:48.000Z","msg":"最近婆婆去左醫院<br />\n照完x光發現有惡性腫瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要已經擴散開去<br />\n醫生同屋企人講話要有心理準備<br />\n聽到果下我都呆左<br />\n個腦一片空白 咩都唸唔到<br />\n跟住想去探佢 但又唔比入去 淨係可以係門口擺低野<br />\n老人家又無電話 打比佢問候幾句又唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要新年果陣見佢 都行得走得無事<br />\n點知唔夠一個月就變到咁<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知有咩可以做到<br />\n有無巴絲可以指點下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經幾日無哂心情又無胃口<br />\n想陪佢又陪唔到... 又打唔到電話問佢點<br />\n婆婆咁多年都好關心我 照顧我<br />\n但係佢最需要人陪既時候 我就咩都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72451bbc20d0c86f0ea95fa617216216d71c5d4a","tid":1911341,"uid":119217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:26:31.000Z","msg":"sorry，想問問點解會唔入得去？"},{"pid":"ed4796a0c38db58ba83ad8e307b429a7aaa3b14d","tid":1911341,"uid":302236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:26:40.000Z","msg":"寫張心意卡畀佢 將相貼返之前你同佢一齊嘅相 再寫啲野多謝佢一直以黎照顧你"},{"pid":"44c9ac80cecf7ada95614e6ed15525720d63a17f","tid":1911341,"uid":302236,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"72451bbc20d0c86f0ea95fa617216216d71c5d4a","tid":1911341,"uid":119217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:26:31.000Z","msg":"sorry，想問問點解會唔入得去？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:26:50.000Z","msg":"武肺"},{"pid":"3aee84788364d2e33be232b807cbd94952ff91b5","tid":1911341,"uid":302236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed4796a0c38db58ba83ad8e307b429a7aaa3b14d","tid":1911341,"uid":302236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:26:40.000Z"